      "title": "Gas shortage to be resolved this month - Litro.",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Litro Gas expects the gas shortage issue to be resolved by the end of this month.",
        "Litro Chairman Muditha Peiris told Daily Mirror online that further gas shipments are scheduled to arrive in the country this month.",
        "\u201cWe expect the crisis to be fully resolved by the end of this month,\u201d he said.",
        "He said that around 6-7 gas shipments are expected in Sri Lanka by the end of July.",
        "The Chairman said that the company has been able to secure the required USD to import the gas."
      ],
